ong_Kong" title="List of banks in Hong Kong" id="mwAyM">deposit taking companies</a> rather than as banks in Hong Kong.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-15" id="cite_note-15"><a href="./Bank#cite_ref-15" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-15" class="mw-reference-text">e.g. Tyree's Banking Law in New Zealand, A L Tyree, LexisNexis 2003, p. 70.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-16" id="cite_note-16"><a href="./Bank#cite_ref-16" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-16" class="mw-reference-text">Bank of England statistics and the book "Where does money come from?", p. 47, by the New Economics Foundation.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-17" id="cite_note-17"><a href="./Bank#cite_ref-17" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-17" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt51" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"https://www.gobankingrates.com/banking/banks/how-banks-make-money/"},"title":{"wt":"How Do Banks Make Money?"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAyQ"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://www.gobankingrates.com/banking/banks/how-banks-make-money/" id="mwAyU">"How Do Banks Make Money?"</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=How+Do+Banks+Make+Money%3F&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gobankingrates.com%2Fbanking%2Fbanks%2Fhow-banks-make-money%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABank" class="Z3988" about="#mwt51" id="mwAyY"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt51" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body